# Additional prettier ignores used ONLY by the root project's format /
# format-check / lint scripts (passed as a second --ignore-path alongside
# .prettierignore). Workspace packages format their own files via their
# own per-package nx targets; excluding them here keeps the root project's
# nx target from overlapping with the workspace packages' targets so
# `nx run-many` can parallelize without two projects touching the same file.

